data.description: Welcome to this lovely, open floor plan, 4bedroom, 3bath home located in Woodcreek subdivision in Fate! As you enter, you'll find a  bedroom, a full bathroom, and an office or study conveniently located at the front of the house, ideal for guests or a home workspace. The primary bedroom is  situated at the back of the home, ensuring more privacy. It boasts ample space, natural light, and a walk in closet. The heart of this home is its eat-in kitchen, complete with stainless steel appliances, island and granite countertops. Outside, enjoy a covered patio where you can unwind. There's also additional storage space to keep your belongings organized. With its functional layout, modern amenities, and prime location, this home offers the blend of comfort, convenience, and style. Don't miss your opportunity to make it yours! PLEAE MAKE SURE TO CHECKOUT THE 3D MODEL AND FLOORPLAN.
